high_descs: walk out of the bedroom and in to the living room.
Get the knife and go to the bathroom in front of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, wash it and then remove it.
Take the knife back into the living room and stand in front of the coffeetable.
Put the knife on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Take the knife and clean it before putting it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around to exit the room and turn left to reach the shelf.
Pick up the knife from the shelf.
Turn around and head left to reach the bathroom to face the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink and take it out.
Turn left and turn right to reach the coffee table on the left.
Put the knife on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed knife on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to the doorway on your right, then hang a right and head towards the shelf on your right near the sofa
Pick up the knife from the the shelf
Turn right and head towards the tv stand, then hang a right and cross the room, and go to the bathroom to your left, head to the sink
Put the knife into the sink, wash it off, then pick it back up
Go to the doorway to your left and hang a right, then go to the coffee table to your right near the sofa
Put the knife on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on a coffee table
